<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>At scf1 and scf2, I never saw a double damage crit. Is this what everyone else is seeing also?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->That's the way the ability was designed. scf1 lets you crit for 33%, scf2 for 66%, scf3 for 100%.<br>
